NAME
       texconfig - configures teTeX

SYNOPSIS
       texconfig

DESCRIPTION
       texconfig  allows  to  configure	 and maintain teTeX in an
       easy and convenient manner. It uses the dialog program  to
       draw  nice  input boxes. After answering the dialoges, the
       appropriate files are changed automatically and all neces-
       sary steps are involved to apply the new settings.

SEE ALSO
       dialog(1),  initex(1),  mf(1),  vi(1), EDITOR environment-
       variable.

